<div class="description col-md-9">
<p>Land Army is a project run by Manchester's Kindling Trust, providing support to new growers during the difficult first few years in the business. The project has been running for several years and has proven itself a successful endeavour, and with increasing ambitions required a logo to improve brand memorability.</p>
<p>Using a boot print and a shovel as inspiration, I designed this logo to reflect the hard work done by the volunteers. The colours are in keeping with the Kindling Trusts branding in general and I think it lends itself to this logo perfectly giving an impression of sun & mud and highlighting the separation between the two words at the toe end of the boot.</p>
